divs: Sighting DetailsHello, i am here in Albuquerque New Mexico, I was on the way to my parents house right around the corner from my house at 10:33 pm Wednsday November 23rd 2011 and i seen a fireball in the sky that was moving very slow then stopped, whatever it was was dripping trails of burning ? underneath it- i stopped at the street corner for about two minutes and just watched the object - i was just making a quick trip to my parents house and did not even have my phone with me to take a pic unfortunatley. i took off around the corner and got to my parents house and brought my dad outside to witness it as well, we were both really suprised what we were seeing and then some clouds got in the way. What was this? I would love to find out!?
Summary: Red Stationary Fireball in sky dripping fire trails, did not move then gained altitude
